org.eclipse.scada.vi.model

Interface VisualInterfacePackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    VisualInterfacePackage

    public static interface VisualInterfacePackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
